  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cosmic Coliseum</strong> is an Action-shooter roguelite where you must fight your way to victory in a Galactic Gladiator Tournament. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/7a357f4598cca21ef6c7eb519edc560e.webp?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/ad2c42fccd4e8962df3744bee79b1928.poster.avif?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/ad2c42fccd4e8962df3744bee79b1928.webm?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>Choose your champion and then battle to survive wave after wave of grueling combat as The Overlords send their vicious alien hordes into the arena to destroy you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/204f17392e8018f6a6ac111c4bb4c7b8.webp?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/06eed55ab5268892b9661cc42738bd30.poster.avif?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/06eed55ab5268892b9661cc42738bd30.webm?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/06eed55ab5268892b9661cc42738bd30.mp4?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Gather XP from your fallen enemies and level-up to gain access to a huge range of upgrades that will unlock advanced weapons and enhanced abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/9d4c3d63bf0b9db7ae25f5ecc4977f4f.webp?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=60 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/e0cc3f67c3c112d4850a072a0c43ff43.poster.avif?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/e0cc3f67c3c112d4850a072a0c43ff43.webm?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/e0cc3f67c3c112d4850a072a0c43ff43.mp4?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Defeat the Overlord Champions to access special bonus power-ups</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Choose from a range of dynamic characters, weapons and unique secondary skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Collect cash to spend at the Arena Shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Destroy each Overlord Boss to unlock the next arena as you grow stronger and more experienced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Accumulate meta-currency with each kill and use it to purchase weapons and characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Combine all of your skills and abilities as you forge a path to victory and become the <strong>Ultimate Champion</strong> of the <strong>Cosmic Coliseum.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.poster.avif?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.webm?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.mp4?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
