ass=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.poster.avif?t=1747350002\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.webm?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2158810/extras/aa907eda321c46a8f5f0f25a049bb700.mp4?t=1747350002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
